#: ../../source/tutorials/2.0-get-data.md:1
msgid "获取并管理金融数据"
msgstr "Acquire and manage financial data"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.0-get-data.md:3
msgid "`qteasy`是一个完全本地化部署和运行的量化交易分析工具包，具备以下功能："
msgstr "`qteasy` is a fully locally deployed and run quantitative trading analysis toolkit with the following features:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.0-get-data.md:5
msgid "金融数据的获取、清洗、存储以及处理、可视化、使用"
msgstr "Acquisition, cleaning, storage, processing, visualization, and use of financial data"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.0-get-data.md:6
msgid "量化交易策略的创建，并提供大量内置基本交易策略"
msgstr "Creation of quantitative trading strategies, with a large number of built-in basic trading strategies provided"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.0-get-data.md:7
msgid "向量化的高速交易策略回测及交易结果评价"
msgstr "Vectorized high-speed backtesting of trading strategies and evaluation of trading results"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.0-get-data.md:8
msgid "交易策略参数的优化以及评价"
msgstr "Optimization and evaluation of trading strategy parameters"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.0-get-data.md:9
msgid "交易策略的部署、实盘运行"
msgstr "Deployment and live trading of trading strategies"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.0-get-data.md:11
msgid "通过本系列教程，您将会通过一系列的实际示例，充分了解`qteasy`的主要功能以及使用方法。"
msgstr "Through this tutorial series, you will gain a thorough understanding of `qteasy`’s main features and how to use them through a series of practical examples."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.0-get-data.md:13
msgid "开始前的准备工作"
msgstr "Preparations before you begin"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.0-get-data.md:15
msgid "在开始本教程前，请完成以下工作："
msgstr "Before starting this tutorial, please complete the following:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.0-get-data.md:17
msgid "完成`qteasy`的安装并升级到最新版本"
msgstr "Complete the installation of `qteasy` and upgrade to the latest version"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.0-get-data.md:18
msgid "注册`tushare pro`账户并确保有一定的积分（大多数高级数据需要较多积分才能下载）"
msgstr "Register a `tushare pro` account and make sure you have enough points (most advanced data requires more points to download)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.0-get-data.md:19
msgid "完成`qteasy.cfg`文件的配置，将`tushare_token`写入配置文件"
msgstr "Complete the configuration of the `qteasy.cfg` file and write `tushare_token` into the configuration file"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.0-get-data.md:20
msgid "完成`mysql`数据库的配置，并将数据库配置写入`qteasy.cfg·`(***可选项***)"
msgstr "Complete the configuration of the `mysql` database and write the database configuration into `qteasy.cfg·` (***optional***)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.0-get-data.md:21
msgid "完成`ta-lib`的安装 (***可选项***)"
msgstr "Complete the installation of `ta-lib` (***optional***)"

