msgid "在这里插入图片描述"
msgstr "Insert image description here"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.0-get-data.md:40
msgid "如果不使用`jupyter notebook`，也可以使用`ipython`："
msgstr "If you don’t use `jupyter notebook`, you can also use `ipython`:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.0-get-data.md:44
msgid "`ipython` 运行在terminal中，但是对图表的支持没有那么好"
